1
00:00:01,010 --> 00:00:03,850
<i>LOVE AND REDEMPTION</i>

2
00:00:04,400 --> 00:00:06,640
<i>EPISODE 8</i>

3
00:02:08,200 --> 00:02:11,079
Give up. You can’t pass. I am you.

4
00:02:11,080 --> 00:02:13,891
Hurting me will only hurt yourself.

5
00:02:43,440 --> 00:02:45,270
Give up!

6
00:02:45,271 --> 00:02:47,351
Why do you have to
torture yourself like this?

7
00:02:58,720 --> 00:03:00,397
Xuan Ji.

8
00:03:00,398 --> 00:03:03,039
The last stage of 13 Punishments
is right in front of me.

9
00:03:03,600 --> 00:03:06,007
I’ve expended too much of
my energy before this.

10
00:03:06,582 --> 00:03:08,645
But it’s alright.

11
00:03:08,646 --> 00:03:10,046
I will go out.

12
00:03:10,640 --> 00:03:13,059
I won’t be defeated here.

13
00:03:56,680 --> 00:03:58,359
Si Feng.

14
00:03:58,360 --> 00:04:01,319
You are indeed my best disciple.

15
00:04:01,320 --> 00:04:02,399
All these years,

16
00:04:02,400 --> 00:04:06,972
there are only a few who survived
the 13 Punishments.

17
00:04:06,973 --> 00:04:08,113
Master.

18
00:04:08,114 --> 00:04:10,741
No wonder you can ignore the palace rules.

19
00:04:10,742 --> 00:04:13,957
Since you’ve reached
the last stage of 13 Punishments,

20
00:04:13,958 --> 00:04:16,438
you just need to make a choice.

21
00:04:17,990 --> 00:04:21,270
Just wear this mask in front of you

22
00:04:22,398 --> 00:04:24,722
and you’ll be able to regain your freedom

23
00:04:25,240 --> 00:04:27,333
and return to Lize Palace.

24
00:04:27,334 --> 00:04:28,416
Hurry up.

25
00:04:29,479 --> 00:04:31,319
Wear the mask.

26
00:04:31,320 --> 00:04:32,647
This is

27
00:04:34,520 --> 00:04:36,349
the Loveless Mask?

28
00:04:36,350 --> 00:04:37,645
You are right.

29
00:04:37,646 --> 00:04:40,164
This is the Loveless Mask.

30
00:04:41,246 --> 00:04:46,679
The person who wears this mask
will have to be heartless and loveless

31
00:04:46,680 --> 00:04:48,160
from now on.

32
00:04:52,767 --> 00:04:54,676
Heartless and loveless.

33
00:04:54,677 --> 00:04:58,501
After you wear this mask,
you have to abandon all of your feelings.

34
00:04:58,502 --> 00:05:02,959
Or else, this Loveless Mask
will take root inside your body.

35
00:05:02,960 --> 00:05:06,679
Every time you are hurt
emotionally, you’ll be cursed.

36
00:05:06,680 --> 00:05:08,879
After three times, you’ll die.

37
00:05:08,880 --> 00:05:14,239
It means that you are exchanging
your feelings for your freedom.

38
00:05:15,518 --> 00:05:17,967
You are just getting rid of
your emotions and feelings.

39
00:05:20,960 --> 00:05:26,239
Compared to suffering in the 13
Punishments forever, this is nothing.

40
00:05:26,240 --> 00:05:27,518
Hurry up.

41
00:05:27,519 --> 00:05:29,839
Hurry up and wear the mask.

42
00:05:29,840 --> 00:05:32,438
Humans are not objects.
How can we be emotionless?

43
00:05:32,439 --> 00:05:34,759
If you want me to live
like an ice forever,

44
00:05:34,760 --> 00:05:36,759
how’s that different from being a zombie?

45
00:05:36,760 --> 00:05:38,429
Si Feng.

46
00:05:38,430 --> 00:05:40,340
Stop being so stubborn anymore.

47
00:05:40,341 --> 00:05:41,941
Listen to me.

48
00:05:42,686 --> 00:05:48,334
Wear the Loveless Mask and
become someone without any emotions.

49
00:05:48,335 --> 00:05:51,523
That way, I can protect you forever.

50
00:05:52,268 --> 00:05:53,546
Master.

51
00:05:54,400 --> 00:05:55,755
I don’t understand.

52
00:05:56,760 --> 00:06:00,621
Why does Lize Palace want to shackle us
from our own emotions?

53
00:06:00,622 --> 00:06:02,727
Why can’t we be like other sects?

54
00:06:02,728 --> 00:06:06,199
Why can’t we form bonds to
support and love each other?

55
00:06:06,200 --> 00:06:09,000
What’s wrong with living like
a real human with real emotions?

56
00:06:09,510 --> 00:06:10,845
I won’t wear

57
00:06:11,360 --> 00:06:13,788
- this mask.
- Insolent fool!

58
00:06:13,789 --> 00:06:15,719
If I ask you to wear it, wear it.

59
00:06:15,720 --> 00:06:20,320
Or else, you’ll never get out from
this 13 Punishments Lianyu Pagoda.

60
00:06:21,007 --> 00:06:24,119
Little Si Feng, wear the mask.

61
00:06:24,120 --> 00:06:26,611
This is not a normal virtual land.

62
00:06:27,522 --> 00:06:29,999
Are you going to be stubborn
until the end?

63
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:34,141
Si Feng, you are born with talents
that others can only dream for.

64
00:06:34,142 --> 00:06:36,830
But you are wasting it like this.
Such a disappointment!

65
00:06:36,831 --> 00:06:38,730
You want to choose feelings?

66
00:06:39,583 --> 00:06:43,137
But do you know what feelings are?

67
00:06:43,800 --> 00:06:47,000
How long can feelings last?

68
00:06:47,920 --> 00:06:50,484
Feelings are just lies!

69
00:06:53,039 --> 00:06:55,559
The Loveless Mask
is right in front of you.

70
00:06:55,560 --> 00:06:57,639
Think about it carefully.

71
00:06:57,640 --> 00:06:59,339
If you don’t wear it,

72
00:06:59,840 --> 00:07:03,611
you’ll stay inside here forever!

73
00:07:18,317 --> 00:07:21,943
If I can come in, I
can definitely get out.

74
00:07:22,895 --> 00:07:25,152
I’ll find a way to get out.

75
00:07:27,406 --> 00:07:29,206
Go ahead and try then.

76
00:07:59,600 --> 00:08:00,959
Senior.

77
00:08:00,960 --> 00:08:02,877
You haven’t improved at all.

78
00:08:02,878 --> 00:08:05,435
- Are you slacking off lately again?
- No.

79
00:08:07,280 --> 00:08:10,759
But I remember you said that
the Five Elements Spell

80
00:08:10,760 --> 00:08:13,960
requires the caster to feel the spirits
of the five elements in this world.

81
00:08:14,640 --> 00:08:18,527
Maybe I can’t improve
because all of my six senses

82
00:08:18,528 --> 00:08:22,312
- are undeveloped and I can’t feel them.
- Nonsense.

83
00:08:22,313 --> 00:08:24,259
You just need to train hard.

84
00:08:49,280 --> 00:08:51,159
<i>MIRROR OF ORIGIN</i>

85
00:08:51,160 --> 00:08:53,043
Mirror of Origin?

86
00:08:53,600 --> 00:08:55,495
This is what the merman told me.

87
00:09:04,040 --> 00:09:05,527
I...

88
00:09:14,375 --> 00:09:15,795
Senior!

89
00:09:17,440 --> 00:09:19,946
Why wouldn’t you let me read that book?

90
00:09:20,920 --> 00:09:22,359
Why do you want to read it?

91
00:09:22,360 --> 00:09:23,799
Because the book stated that

92
00:09:23,800 --> 00:09:26,317
the Mirror of Origin can help me
get back my six senses.

93
00:09:26,318 --> 00:09:27,920
So, I want to read about it.

94
00:09:30,680 --> 00:09:32,079
Who told you about it?

95
00:09:32,080 --> 00:09:33,441
It’s...

96
00:09:34,320 --> 00:09:35,919
I heard it from someone.

97
00:09:35,920 --> 00:09:38,038
So, I want to give it a try.

98
00:09:38,039 --> 00:09:39,893
Listen to me, Xuan Ji.

99
00:09:39,894 --> 00:09:42,989
You are not allowed to investigate about
Mirror of Origin anymore.

100
00:09:42,990 --> 00:09:46,560
Why are you so mad?
I just want to become a normal human.

101
00:09:46,561 --> 00:09:48,718
I want to feel what
normal people can feel.

102
00:09:48,719 --> 00:09:52,663
- What did I do wrong?
- I’ve told you many times.

103
00:09:52,664 --> 00:09:54,924
You shouldn’t care about
having the six senses or not.

104
00:09:54,925 --> 00:09:56,799
But you are still distracted with that by

105
00:09:56,800 --> 00:09:59,912
readings books that you shouldn’t.
You don’t know what you did wrong?

106
00:10:01,095 --> 00:10:04,490
Looks like I have to
punish you for real today.

107
00:10:04,491 --> 00:10:06,119
Go to the back of the mountain
to chop down the bamboos.

108
00:10:06,120 --> 00:10:09,239
You are not allowed to eat
until you’ve chopped them down.

109
00:10:09,240 --> 00:10:10,476
I...

110
00:10:11,280 --> 00:10:13,170
Senior Hao Chen, you...

111
00:12:00,120 --> 00:12:02,160
You are as stubborn as ever.

112
00:12:02,800 --> 00:12:05,519
As long as I can wipe off your memory
about the Mirror of Origin,

113
00:12:05,520 --> 00:12:07,688
you won’t be obsessed with it anymore.

114
00:12:21,640 --> 00:12:24,989
Looks like I really can’t use any of
my power in the mortal realm.

115
00:12:25,862 --> 00:12:29,315
The trial that you’ll face in
this lifetime will be your last chance.

116
00:12:31,080 --> 00:12:32,639
Xuan Ji.

117
00:12:32,640 --> 00:12:36,239
What can I do to
protect you in this life

118
00:12:36,240 --> 00:12:38,289
so that you can pass
the trial without problem?

119
00:13:09,760 --> 00:13:11,079
What is it?

120
00:13:11,080 --> 00:13:12,815
Are you still angry at me?

121
00:13:12,816 --> 00:13:14,119
I wouldn’t dare.

122
00:13:14,120 --> 00:13:17,639
I just want to get this done earlier
so that I can eat.

123
00:13:17,640 --> 00:13:19,302
No need to chop anymore.

124
00:13:19,303 --> 00:13:21,269
I was too strict that day.

125
00:13:21,270 --> 00:13:23,225
I shouldn’t have blamed everything on you.

126
00:13:24,840 --> 00:13:26,342
Xuan Ji.

127
00:13:26,343 --> 00:13:27,829
You don’t know about it.

128
00:13:27,830 --> 00:13:31,079
But this Mirror of Origin
is an evil mirror.

129
00:13:31,080 --> 00:13:33,439
Not only it can’t help you
recover your six senses,

130
00:13:33,440 --> 00:13:36,822
it can even bewitch you
and mess with your mind.

131
00:13:37,671 --> 00:13:39,440
How is that possible?

132
00:13:41,129 --> 00:13:44,279
This mirror will use the demon
and obsession in your heart

133
00:13:44,280 --> 00:13:48,434
to put you into an imaginary
land and feed on your soul.

134
00:13:48,435 --> 00:13:52,039
If someone urges you
to look for that Mirror of Origin,

135
00:13:52,040 --> 00:13:54,560
I’m afraid that the person
must have an ulterior motive.

136
00:13:59,480 --> 00:14:04,973
I know that having no six
senses bothers you a lot.

137
00:14:05,726 --> 00:14:07,901
I was too emotional that day.

138
00:14:07,902 --> 00:14:09,959
I just want to tell you that

139
00:14:09,960 --> 00:14:12,525
your six senses won’t
affect anything in your life.

140
00:14:12,526 --> 00:14:16,565
But sometimes,
I’ll feel like a freak.

141
00:14:18,160 --> 00:14:21,119
Extraordinary people are
always born different.

142
00:14:21,120 --> 00:14:25,434
Although you don’t have six senses,
you can smell the demonic aura.

143
00:14:25,435 --> 00:14:28,625
Although you can’t tell whether
a sound is pleasant or not,

144
00:14:28,626 --> 00:14:30,976
you can hear the sound of demons.

145
00:14:31,646 --> 00:14:33,309
It means that

146
00:14:33,310 --> 00:14:36,559
you are born with the talents
to hunt monsters and demons.

147
00:14:36,560 --> 00:14:41,279
You are destined to be the
protector of the secret ground.

148
00:14:41,280 --> 00:14:43,159
You just need to remember this.

149
00:14:43,160 --> 00:14:46,814
Then, you won’t have to care
about what you don’t have.

150
00:14:49,160 --> 00:14:50,718
But...

151
00:14:52,680 --> 00:14:57,836
No matter you have six
senses or not, you are just you.

152
00:14:57,837 --> 00:14:59,399
People who really care about you

153
00:14:59,400 --> 00:15:02,542
won’t treat you differently just because
you are not the same.

154
00:15:02,543 --> 00:15:07,110
In my heart, you’ll always be
the unique Xuan Ji that I know.

155
00:15:09,560 --> 00:15:12,605
Senior Hao Chen,
I was too impulsive that day.

156
00:15:12,606 --> 00:15:14,332
I shouldn’t have butted head with you.

157
00:15:16,319 --> 00:15:20,269
Listen to me. Don’t think about
those unnecessary things.

158
00:15:20,270 --> 00:15:22,462
And don’t look for that Mirror of Origin.

159
00:15:23,120 --> 00:15:26,480
I don’t want you to be used by
those who bear you ill will.

160
00:15:29,040 --> 00:15:32,390
Okay. I promise you, Senior Hao Chen.

161
00:15:38,990 --> 00:15:41,290
You are hungry, right? You little glutton.

162
00:15:50,560 --> 00:15:52,970
So many delicious food! Senior Hao Chen.

163
00:15:52,971 --> 00:15:55,692
Didn’t you say that I cannot eat too full?

164
00:15:55,693 --> 00:15:58,879
Why did you buy so much
delicious food for me today?

165
00:15:58,880 --> 00:16:02,040
Have you forgotten that
it’s your birthday today?

166
00:16:05,520 --> 00:16:09,068
That’s right. When it was
my birthday in the past,

167
00:16:09,069 --> 00:16:11,247
Ling Long would treat me
to delicious food too.

168
00:16:11,248 --> 00:16:14,328
But back then,
I couldn’t taste anything at all.

169
00:16:15,440 --> 00:16:16,999
By the way, Senior Hao Chen.

170
00:16:17,000 --> 00:16:19,159
Today is Si Feng’s birthday too.

171
00:16:19,160 --> 00:16:21,558
Can you give me that Sound Bell
for a moment?

172
00:16:21,559 --> 00:16:23,799
I want to wish him happy birthday.

173
00:16:26,560 --> 00:16:27,710
Fine.

174
00:16:30,120 --> 00:16:31,408
Eat slowly.

175
00:16:34,084 --> 00:16:36,281
I can only wish him in my heart then.

176
00:16:36,282 --> 00:16:39,879
He’s such a particular person. I’m sure
that he’ll treat his birthday well.

177
00:16:39,880 --> 00:16:42,683
I’m sure that he’ll celebrate it with
good food and drinks.

178
00:16:47,200 --> 00:16:48,486
Xuan Ji.

179
00:16:49,760 --> 00:16:53,320
This is my 353rd day
in this wretched place.

180
00:16:55,102 --> 00:16:56,896
I still can’t pass

181
00:16:57,791 --> 00:16:59,563
this last stage.

182
00:17:01,280 --> 00:17:02,764
And...

183
00:17:03,600 --> 00:17:05,738
I still haven’t heard anything
from you yet.

184
00:17:07,863 --> 00:17:10,031
Maybe that bell is really broken.

185
00:17:12,431 --> 00:17:13,753
Xuan Ji.

186
00:17:14,895 --> 00:17:16,975
I might not be able to
keep my promise anymore.

187
00:17:18,496 --> 00:17:20,462
I really can’t take it anymore.

188
00:17:22,550 --> 00:17:25,710
It’s your birthday today.

189
00:17:27,880 --> 00:17:29,678
I know that you can’t hear me.

190
00:17:31,680 --> 00:17:33,673
Happy birthday.

191
00:17:34,520 --> 00:17:36,498
I wish that you can live happily forever.

192
00:17:37,960 --> 00:17:41,283
I wish that you can live
your life freely however you like it.

193
00:17:43,200 --> 00:17:44,650
Senior Hao Chen.

194
00:17:45,894 --> 00:17:49,733
Senior Hao Chen, this is the nectar
that I brewed myself.

195
00:17:49,734 --> 00:17:52,862
I put a lot of effort into it.
Please accept it.

196
00:17:52,863 --> 00:17:54,526
Thank you for your kindness.

197
00:17:54,527 --> 00:17:56,559
Since you’ve put a lot of effort into it,

198
00:17:56,560 --> 00:17:58,217
you should keep it for yourself.

199
00:17:59,160 --> 00:18:00,679
Senior Hao Chen.

200
00:18:00,680 --> 00:18:03,873
All these years, can’t you tell about
the feelings I have for you?

201
00:18:03,874 --> 00:18:06,157
- Actually, I...
- If it’s pointless, don’t say it.

202
00:18:06,158 --> 00:18:09,089
You won’t even give me
a chance to confess?

203
00:18:11,560 --> 00:18:13,907
I’m cultivating the Heartless Path.

204
00:18:13,908 --> 00:18:18,279
Whether you say it out or
not, it doesn’t matter to me.

205
00:18:19,166 --> 00:18:20,325
Senior.

206
00:18:20,326 --> 00:18:25,477
Although you look so gentlemanly
and gentle on the surface,

207
00:18:25,478 --> 00:18:30,019
you are actually a
cruel and cold person!

208
00:18:30,880 --> 00:18:35,000
Besides Xuan Ji, you’ve never
cared about other people at all!

209
00:18:37,520 --> 00:18:38,828
Come out.

210
00:18:41,200 --> 00:18:42,891
You eavesdrop on people now?

211
00:18:50,120 --> 00:18:54,520
There will be a way out.

212
00:18:56,640 --> 00:18:58,458
I don’t believe it.

213
00:18:59,407 --> 00:19:03,643
So, the one Senior Duan Qing likes is you?

214
00:19:03,644 --> 00:19:05,279
Why didn’t you accept her?

215
00:19:05,280 --> 00:19:07,932
I think Senior Duan Qing is quite nice.

216
00:19:10,390 --> 00:19:12,037
Haven’t I told you before?

217
00:19:12,038 --> 00:19:13,797
We are on the Heartless Path.

218
00:19:13,798 --> 00:19:15,375
We cannot love someone.

219
00:19:16,400 --> 00:19:18,239
I know.

220
00:19:18,240 --> 00:19:21,512
But don’t you want someone to love?

221
00:19:23,399 --> 00:19:27,079
Only the path I’ve chosen
is the right one. The rest is unimportant.

222
00:19:27,080 --> 00:19:28,693
You can’t be distracted.

223
00:19:28,694 --> 00:19:31,254
So stay focus and say no more.

224
00:19:34,471 --> 00:19:36,479
Since it’s your birthday today,

225
00:19:36,480 --> 00:19:39,360
I’ll make another exception
to let you drink today.

226
00:19:40,120 --> 00:19:42,646
Wait here. I’ll get the grape wine.

227
00:19:47,647 --> 00:19:50,039
I think my stuffs are in this library too.

228
00:19:50,040 --> 00:19:53,446
I should find the Sound Bell
and have a talk with Si Feng.

229
00:20:18,934 --> 00:20:22,911
Si Feng.

230
00:20:26,440 --> 00:20:29,195
- Si Feng!
- Junior.

231
00:20:30,600 --> 00:20:32,221
What are you doing?

232
00:20:32,222 --> 00:20:33,393
I...

233
00:20:34,480 --> 00:20:36,039
Senior.

234
00:20:36,040 --> 00:20:39,159
I don’t understand what you said just now.

235
00:20:39,160 --> 00:20:42,526
So, I want to ask my friend about it
through the Sound Bell.

236
00:20:43,134 --> 00:20:46,331
You don’t know what love means.
Don’t think too much.

237
00:20:46,332 --> 00:20:49,405
Says who? I have someone I like too.

238
00:20:50,480 --> 00:20:52,115
I like Sixth Senior.

239
00:20:53,040 --> 00:20:56,079
Min Yan? You like Min Yan?

240
00:20:56,080 --> 00:20:59,872
Let me tell you. I’ve collected
a lot of fruits for Sixth Senior.

241
00:20:59,873 --> 00:21:01,399
Senior Duan Qing told me that

242
00:21:01,400 --> 00:21:04,298
I have to share the things that I like
with the one whom I like.

243
00:21:07,167 --> 00:21:09,599
Why are you laughing?

244
00:21:09,600 --> 00:21:12,999
You’ve come here for so long and this is
the first time you mentioned about him.

245
00:21:13,000 --> 00:21:14,560
What’s wrong with that?

246
00:21:15,988 --> 00:21:19,361
You don’t even know
what you are talking about.

247
00:21:27,126 --> 00:21:28,404
Did you hear that?

248
00:21:28,974 --> 00:21:30,839
What did I say?

249
00:21:30,840 --> 00:21:33,616
You are struggling so hard here

250
00:21:33,617 --> 00:21:36,270
to keep that vague and insubstantial love.

251
00:21:36,271 --> 00:21:38,511
And you put yourself
into such a bad shape.

252
00:21:39,080 --> 00:21:41,440
But what do you get?

253
00:21:43,239 --> 00:21:45,399
This is just a one-sided love.

254
00:21:45,400 --> 00:21:48,559
She doesn’t even care about you.

255
00:21:48,560 --> 00:21:50,320
You were never in

256
00:21:51,680 --> 00:21:54,117
Chu Xuan Ji’s heart at all.

257
00:21:55,040 --> 00:21:57,119
The feelings in this world

258
00:21:57,120 --> 00:22:00,113
are the coldest and
the most illusory things

259
00:22:01,726 --> 00:22:03,879
in this world.

260
00:22:08,134 --> 00:22:10,174
Don’t you know

261
00:22:11,760 --> 00:22:14,541
who you are?

262
00:22:14,542 --> 00:22:18,990
You shouldn’t have
dabbled in love at all!

263
00:22:19,680 --> 00:22:24,032
Lize Palace is your one true destiny.

264
00:22:28,607 --> 00:22:31,480
I’ve given you one year.

265
00:22:32,120 --> 00:22:34,314
I think you get it now.

266
00:22:36,680 --> 00:22:38,622
Wear the Loveless Mask.

267
00:22:38,623 --> 00:22:41,665
And you’ll still be
the first pupil of Lize Palace.

268
00:22:42,567 --> 00:22:46,076
And you’ll still be my
successor in the future.

269
00:22:46,774 --> 00:22:50,494
If others dare comment about it,

270
00:22:51,680 --> 00:22:53,240
I’ll kill them.

271
00:22:57,911 --> 00:22:59,183
Si Feng.

272
00:22:59,880 --> 00:23:03,326
You still can’t let go of
those insubstantial feelings?

273
00:23:12,920 --> 00:23:14,168
Fine.

274
00:23:14,960 --> 00:23:19,112
Don’t blame me
for forcing you then!

275
00:23:27,720 --> 00:23:29,199
Brother Liu.

276
00:23:29,200 --> 00:23:32,599
Liu Yi Huan is a traitor.

277
00:23:32,600 --> 00:23:37,919
The rope on him will descend
two feet every two hours.

278
00:23:37,920 --> 00:23:43,149
At midnight, he’ll fall into the
poisonous swamp below him

279
00:23:43,150 --> 00:23:45,630
and be disintegrated whole.

280
00:23:46,318 --> 00:23:47,581
Master.

281
00:23:48,167 --> 00:23:51,542
I’m the one who broke the rules.
You should punish me instead.

282
00:23:51,543 --> 00:23:54,439
This has nothing to do with Brother Liu.
Let him go!

283
00:23:54,440 --> 00:23:57,599
Liu Yi Huan is
the criminal of Lize Palace.

284
00:23:57,600 --> 00:23:59,159
But he tried to escape.

285
00:23:59,160 --> 00:24:02,719
We caught him and now,
he’ll be punished to death.

286
00:24:02,720 --> 00:24:06,160
But since you are pleading on his behalf,

287
00:24:06,903 --> 00:24:08,824
I can spare him.

288
00:24:11,800 --> 00:24:14,599
I think you know what I mean.

289
00:24:14,600 --> 00:24:18,405
He’s at Houyuan Bell Room
inside Fengqi Hall.

290
00:24:18,406 --> 00:24:21,519
If you want to save him, the only way

291
00:24:22,080 --> 00:24:25,859
is to wear this Loveless Mask
and walk out from this place.

292
00:24:26,678 --> 00:24:28,150
Let me remind you.

293
00:24:28,151 --> 00:24:30,168
After midnight,

294
00:24:30,711 --> 00:24:33,351
your friend will turn into a corpse.

295
00:24:50,440 --> 00:24:51,879
I am Chu Xuan Ji.

296
00:24:51,880 --> 00:24:54,891
You are my first friend from
outside of Shaoyang.

297
00:24:54,892 --> 00:24:56,399
It’s your birthday today.

298
00:24:56,400 --> 00:24:58,719
So, I made a birthday cake for you.

299
00:24:58,720 --> 00:25:01,290
Ling Long said that we are destined
to meet each other.

300
00:25:05,812 --> 00:25:08,479
I really didn’t know how I fell here.

301
00:25:08,480 --> 00:25:13,079
And then... And
then, I can’t fly.

302
00:25:13,080 --> 00:25:15,039
What are you doing?

303
00:25:15,040 --> 00:25:17,559
Your shirt is dirty.
Let me clean it for you.

304
00:25:17,560 --> 00:25:19,079
Don’t touch me.

305
00:25:19,080 --> 00:25:23,519
How can you talk like this?

306
00:25:23,520 --> 00:25:26,719
I’m sorry. I didn’t mean to
knock over your tea.

307
00:25:26,720 --> 00:25:29,840
Why is it always you?

308
00:25:38,773 --> 00:25:41,213
- Little Stammer, do you feel very hot?
- I...

309
00:25:41,720 --> 00:25:43,711
- No.
- No?

310
00:25:48,120 --> 00:25:50,959
Don’t worry. I have a way
to get pass the Candle Dragon.

311
00:25:50,960 --> 00:25:52,279
We can use this.

312
00:25:52,280 --> 00:25:55,238
This Lightning Truncheon
only allows one person to use it.

313
00:25:55,239 --> 00:25:56,814
But there are two of us.

314
00:25:56,815 --> 00:25:58,784
Just act like we are one.

315
00:26:03,480 --> 00:26:05,886
Don’t move.
I’m going to cast the spell now.

316
00:26:05,887 --> 00:26:07,406
Si Feng, you smiled.

317
00:26:07,407 --> 00:26:09,486
Your smile is so pretty.

318
00:26:09,487 --> 00:26:11,519
Your smile is like this wine.

319
00:26:11,520 --> 00:26:13,959
So, I think you look really good
when you smile.

320
00:26:13,960 --> 00:26:16,399
You have to smile more from now on.
Like this.

321
00:26:16,400 --> 00:26:17,533
Like this.

322
00:26:20,600 --> 00:26:22,752
Don’t you know

323
00:26:23,440 --> 00:26:25,656
who you are?

324
00:26:26,440 --> 00:26:30,919
After midnight, your friend
will turn into a corpse.

325
00:26:35,242 --> 00:26:39,039
I’m here to bring you some dried fruits.
They are very sweet.

326
00:26:39,040 --> 00:26:41,359
You are kneeling.
After eating some sweet, dried fruits,

327
00:26:41,360 --> 00:26:44,039
you won’t feel painful anymore. Here.

328
00:26:44,040 --> 00:26:45,639
Don’t worry.

329
00:26:45,640 --> 00:26:47,999
I’ll find those mirror shards for you

330
00:26:48,000 --> 00:26:50,128
so that you can restore your six senses.

331
00:26:50,680 --> 00:26:52,640
It’s a deal then.

332
00:27:05,920 --> 00:27:07,679
It’s a deal then. After four years,

333
00:27:07,680 --> 00:27:10,160
we’ll roam the world and train together.

334
00:27:11,800 --> 00:27:14,010
- You are using saliva again.
- Ling Long said that

335
00:27:14,011 --> 00:27:16,279
this is the most unbreakable vow.

336
00:27:16,280 --> 00:27:17,976
Then, you won’t break your promise.

337
00:28:29,600 --> 00:28:31,919
Brother Liu. Are you alright?

338
00:28:34,009 --> 00:28:35,272
Little Phoenix.

339
00:28:35,273 --> 00:28:37,232
The mask on your face.

340
00:28:37,960 --> 00:28:39,232
It’s fine.

341
00:28:42,440 --> 00:28:44,463
I heard those two monsters.

342
00:28:44,464 --> 00:28:46,554
This is the Loveless Mask.

343
00:28:47,400 --> 00:28:49,117
You did it to save me.

344
00:28:49,800 --> 00:28:52,703
I owe you a big one.

345
00:28:52,704 --> 00:28:54,424
Maybe my master is right.

346
00:28:55,320 --> 00:28:59,560
Love in this world is not
as beautiful as I think it is.

347
00:29:00,200 --> 00:29:01,599
But cutting it away,

348
00:29:01,600 --> 00:29:04,140
it’ll be less painful and
less grudges for myself.

349
00:29:05,680 --> 00:29:08,535
Didn’t you leave Lize Palace
to save your daughter?

350
00:29:08,536 --> 00:29:10,094
How is she?

351
00:29:10,784 --> 00:29:14,399
When I went there, I
could almost save her.

352
00:29:14,400 --> 00:29:17,639
But at that time, she suddenly
disappeared right in front of me.

353
00:29:17,640 --> 00:29:19,319
What is your plan then?

354
00:29:19,320 --> 00:29:22,799
I heard that the heavenly realm
has a celestial eye that sees everything.

355
00:29:22,800 --> 00:29:24,279
As long as I can find Yu’Er,

356
00:29:24,280 --> 00:29:27,611
I’m willing to risk my life
to try and do that.

357
00:30:29,680 --> 00:30:31,479
Who are you?

358
00:30:31,480 --> 00:30:33,055
Where am I?

359
00:30:33,056 --> 00:30:36,007
I’m sure that you’ve heard about
the Sky Hall before.

360
00:30:36,008 --> 00:30:37,088
Sky Hall?

361
00:30:40,240 --> 00:30:41,799
Why did you bring me here?

362
00:30:41,800 --> 00:30:46,279
The five sects
are cornering you like a rat.

363
00:30:46,280 --> 00:30:48,280
Don’t you want to seek revenge?

364
00:30:48,800 --> 00:30:53,202
Since we have the same enemy,
why don’t we work together?

365
00:30:55,072 --> 00:30:56,636
You want to use me?

366
00:30:57,160 --> 00:31:00,360
We’ll have to see if you are
worthy enough to be used by me.

367
00:31:22,400 --> 00:31:24,387
What else can you do now?

368
00:31:29,560 --> 00:31:31,320
Your turn. What’s wrong?

369
00:31:32,512 --> 00:31:35,015
Xuyang Peak must be very cold now.

370
00:31:35,016 --> 00:31:37,787
I wonder if Xuan Ji brought
enough clothes with her or not.

371
00:31:38,320 --> 00:31:41,911
Don’t worry. Xuan Ji
can’t feel the cold anyway.

372
00:31:41,912 --> 00:31:45,286
Look at the board. I took away
five of your chess pieces already.

373
00:31:45,888 --> 00:31:47,039
Little Six,

374
00:31:47,040 --> 00:31:49,560
- I was not paying attention. You can’t...
- Stop playing.

375
00:31:51,624 --> 00:31:53,319
Master asked us to go to
Bamboo Forest Jian

376
00:31:53,320 --> 00:31:55,847
to help him choose some new disciples.

377
00:31:55,848 --> 00:31:57,199
Wait, First Senior.

378
00:31:57,200 --> 00:31:59,599
I don’t believe that
I can’t win Little Six.

379
00:31:59,600 --> 00:32:01,598
I...

380
00:32:02,160 --> 00:32:03,614
I’ll put it here.

381
00:32:08,800 --> 00:32:10,359
So unfortunate.

382
00:32:10,360 --> 00:32:13,821
You could’ve won
another round if you put it...

383
00:32:16,264 --> 00:32:18,399
I don’t want to put it here then.

384
00:32:18,400 --> 00:32:20,012
It’s too late to change.

385
00:32:20,752 --> 00:32:23,839
We have a deal.
Loser has to act like a dog.

386
00:32:23,840 --> 00:32:25,277
Don’t be a sore loser.

387
00:32:26,369 --> 00:32:28,369
How does a dog bark? Do it.

388
00:32:28,969 --> 00:32:30,879
Woof!

389
00:32:30,880 --> 00:32:32,560
I hate you the most!

390
00:32:33,768 --> 00:32:37,039
Ling Long, you said that
you won’t be a sore loser!

391
00:32:37,040 --> 00:32:39,655
Both of you have
never changed since young.

392
00:32:39,656 --> 00:32:41,800
Both of you always quarrel.

393
00:32:47,440 --> 00:32:49,046
<i>PALACE HALL</i>

394
00:32:50,255 --> 00:32:51,896
Greetings, Master.

395
00:32:53,280 --> 00:32:56,233
Master, Xuan Ji can already
break the Barrier Formation.

396
00:32:58,271 --> 00:32:59,703
Xuan Ji.

397
00:32:59,704 --> 00:33:02,350
You are here for four years already.

398
00:33:02,351 --> 00:33:04,871
Now, you’ve improved a lot.

399
00:33:04,872 --> 00:33:06,999
I’m relieved.

400
00:33:07,000 --> 00:33:08,926
According to the rules of the deity,

401
00:33:08,927 --> 00:33:11,119
you are old enough
to start your first trial.

402
00:33:11,120 --> 00:33:14,489
I should let you go back
to Shouyang Peak first.

403
00:33:14,490 --> 00:33:16,008
I can go back to Shouyang Peak?

404
00:33:16,629 --> 00:33:19,079
Then, I can meet Ling Long
and Sixth Senior again.

405
00:33:19,080 --> 00:33:20,679
Awesome!

406
00:33:20,680 --> 00:33:21,959
But remember.

407
00:33:21,960 --> 00:33:26,647
No matter when it is or where
you are, you have to remember

408
00:33:26,648 --> 00:33:29,808
your mission as the disciple
of Xuyang Peak.

409
00:33:30,360 --> 00:33:33,480
Do you mean the protection of
the secret ground?

410
00:33:35,200 --> 00:33:39,487
The secret ground of Shaoyang will
affect the safety of the three realms.

411
00:33:39,488 --> 00:33:42,911
As the protector of the secret ground,

412
00:33:42,912 --> 00:33:45,863
it’s a great responsibility for you.

413
00:33:45,864 --> 00:33:48,476
And it’s not an easy thing
to protect the secret ground.

414
00:33:49,096 --> 00:33:51,759
It’s the most important thing
in your life.

415
00:33:51,760 --> 00:33:54,960
You have to give your everything to it.

416
00:33:55,584 --> 00:33:58,879
Other things will always come second.

417
00:33:58,880 --> 00:34:00,759
You have to be always prepared

418
00:34:00,760 --> 00:34:04,239
to lay down your life
to protect the secret ground.

419
00:34:04,240 --> 00:34:05,453
Understand?

420
00:34:07,440 --> 00:34:08,719
Good.

421
00:34:08,720 --> 00:34:11,680
Today, you’ll make a vow

422
00:34:12,200 --> 00:34:14,992
to protect the secret ground forever

423
00:34:14,993 --> 00:34:17,703
and the safety of the whole world.

424
00:34:17,704 --> 00:34:19,177
Yes, Master.

425
00:34:22,617 --> 00:34:26,504
I, Chu Xuan Ji, vow that I’ll
protect the secret ground forever.

426
00:34:40,520 --> 00:34:42,719
Ling Long. You must be thirsty.

427
00:34:42,720 --> 00:34:45,094
I brought you a cup of tea. Have a taste.

428
00:34:48,240 --> 00:34:50,040
How is it?

429
00:34:51,040 --> 00:34:52,325
It’s not good.

430
00:34:53,720 --> 00:34:54,960
Senior.

431
00:34:55,640 --> 00:34:59,367
Senior, when can you bring me
to Shouyang Peak?

432
00:34:59,368 --> 00:35:01,364
- Shouyang Peak? You...
- Yes.

433
00:35:01,365 --> 00:35:03,559
- Zhong Min Yan, you...
- Senior.

434
00:35:03,560 --> 00:35:05,196
- Senior!
- She...

435
00:35:06,120 --> 00:35:07,755
Senior.

436
00:35:09,111 --> 00:35:11,799
- You...
- When will we go there?

437
00:35:11,800 --> 00:35:13,001
No.

438
00:35:19,880 --> 00:35:21,290
Senior!

439
00:35:22,720 --> 00:35:24,519
- Senior!
- Xuan Ji!

440
00:35:24,520 --> 00:35:25,930
Xuan Ji.

441
00:35:26,520 --> 00:35:28,335
Ling Long, Sixth Senior.

442
00:35:29,560 --> 00:35:31,639
Xuan Ji, what are you doing?

443
00:35:31,640 --> 00:35:34,079
- She is a demon.
- Save me, Senior!

444
00:35:34,080 --> 00:35:35,679
Xuan Ji, you misunderstood her!

445
00:35:35,680 --> 00:35:36,799
No, I didn’t.

446
00:35:36,800 --> 00:35:38,280
Show yourself!

447
00:35:42,840 --> 00:35:44,211
What happened?

448
00:35:44,960 --> 00:35:47,171
- It’s Shadow Demon.
- Let’s go and help her!

449
00:35:49,040 --> 00:35:50,303
Wait!

450
00:35:53,744 --> 00:35:56,335
- Father, Xuan Ji...
- Master, Xuan Ji is in danger.

451
00:35:56,336 --> 00:35:57,920
I want to see

452
00:35:57,921 --> 00:36:01,041
- how much has she improved in four years.
- But...

453
00:36:09,880 --> 00:36:11,528
Xuan Ji, be careful!

454
00:37:11,400 --> 00:37:12,879
- Xuan Ji!
- Xuan Ji!

455
00:37:12,880 --> 00:37:14,172
Ling Long!

456
00:37:17,560 --> 00:37:20,206
You brat. How can you just
come back without any notice?

457
00:37:20,207 --> 00:37:23,679
Do you know how unprepared I am
after not seeing you for four years?

458
00:37:23,680 --> 00:37:25,770
I want to give you a surprise.

459
00:37:25,771 --> 00:37:27,919
This is not a surprise. You scared me.

460
00:37:27,920 --> 00:37:29,879
You fought so many demons alone.

461
00:37:29,880 --> 00:37:31,879
Let me see if you are hurt or not.

462
00:37:31,880 --> 00:37:33,191
I’m fine.

463
00:37:33,192 --> 00:37:35,810
I’ve become strong now.
I can protect you now.

464
00:37:37,024 --> 00:37:41,047
- I really miss you.
- Me too.

465
00:37:41,048 --> 00:37:43,159
- Xuan Ji.
- Junior Xuan Ji.

466
00:37:43,160 --> 00:37:45,240
You fought very well just now.

467
00:37:46,352 --> 00:37:49,450
Sixth Senior, First Senior,
Second Senior, Fifth Senior.

468
00:37:49,451 --> 00:37:51,159
Long time no see.

469
00:37:51,160 --> 00:37:53,210
You are so biased.

470
00:37:53,211 --> 00:37:56,534
How could you call Sixth Senior first
before addressing me and First Senior?

471
00:37:57,920 --> 00:38:00,163
That’s because
I’m her favourite Sixth Senior.

472
00:38:00,880 --> 00:38:02,920
You’ve grown up and become prettier.

473
00:38:03,888 --> 00:38:06,258
Of course. Xuan Ji is a born beauty.

474
00:38:06,259 --> 00:38:09,791
I wonder who it is who kept
holding onto a demon just now.

475
00:38:09,792 --> 00:38:12,239
You kept holding onto a demon.

476
00:38:12,240 --> 00:38:13,931
I didn’t do that.

477
00:38:17,631 --> 00:38:20,519
After fighting the demon just now,
I’m hungry.

478
00:38:20,520 --> 00:38:23,467
You are in luck. We have
Eight Treasures Chicken with Longan

479
00:38:23,468 --> 00:38:25,559
and roasted lamb shank.
They are delicious.

480
00:38:25,560 --> 00:38:28,975
So much food? Stop talking and let’s eat.
I’m hungry. Let’s go.

481
00:38:28,976 --> 00:38:30,315
- Let’s go.
- Let’s go.

482
00:38:33,296 --> 00:38:37,215
Those demons even dare to
try infiltrating into our sect.

483
00:38:37,840 --> 00:38:41,119
You have to check
all the new disciples.

484
00:38:41,120 --> 00:38:45,199
Could it be that the demon clan know that
the thing in Shaoyang secret ground is...

485
00:38:45,200 --> 00:38:47,879
If they are really here
for the secret ground,

486
00:38:47,880 --> 00:38:49,791
they won’t be so easily defeated.

487
00:38:49,792 --> 00:38:54,800
Maybe they are just trying to
install some spies into our sect.

488
00:38:55,440 --> 00:38:59,279
Sect Leader. We’ve been investigating
that Sky Hall for the past four years.

489
00:38:59,280 --> 00:39:01,199
But we couldn’t find anything.

490
00:39:01,200 --> 00:39:03,279
After all, our ancestors and the deities

491
00:39:03,280 --> 00:39:05,255
had annihilated them back then.

492
00:39:05,256 --> 00:39:08,447
Only some weak and
scattered demons are left.

493
00:39:08,448 --> 00:39:09,959
I don’t think they’ll
be able to do anything.

494
00:39:09,960 --> 00:39:11,959
Our ancestor received
an oracle in the past.

495
00:39:11,960 --> 00:39:14,495
It’s said that there will be a calamity
within these 30 years.

496
00:39:14,496 --> 00:39:16,759
Now, 20 years have passed.
We have only 10 more years.

497
00:39:16,760 --> 00:39:18,400
We have to be careful.

498
00:39:20,000 --> 00:39:23,915
Alright. Send someone
to inform all the major sects.

499
00:39:23,916 --> 00:39:25,636
Tell them to be careful.

500
00:39:26,575 --> 00:39:27,766
Yes, Sect Leader.

501
00:39:30,665 --> 00:39:32,985
- Father, we are back!
- Father!

502
00:39:33,840 --> 00:39:35,199
Xuan Ji.

503
00:39:35,200 --> 00:39:36,919
You’ve improved a lot.

504
00:39:36,920 --> 00:39:39,918
Father, you saw me just now?

505
00:39:39,919 --> 00:39:43,959
Father, Xuan Ji can control
the Five Elements Spell with ease now.

506
00:39:43,960 --> 00:39:46,756
Other seniors might not
be able to do that too.

507
00:39:46,757 --> 00:39:48,919
They used to say that
my sister is weak. Now,

508
00:39:48,920 --> 00:39:51,270
we should show them how awesome she is.

509
00:39:52,160 --> 00:39:56,336
Xuan Ji, you are much better
than what I’ve expected.

510
00:39:57,240 --> 00:39:58,679
For the past four years,

511
00:39:58,680 --> 00:40:02,056
Master Heng Yang
was meditating in seclusion.

512
00:40:02,057 --> 00:40:05,702
You were single-handedly
taught by Senior Hao Chen.

513
00:40:05,703 --> 00:40:10,070
To find great teacher and
good friends in life are difficult.

514
00:40:10,071 --> 00:40:14,399
You are really blessed and lucky
to have met Senior Hao Chen.

515
00:40:14,400 --> 00:40:16,959
Don’t ever forget about his kindness
for teaching you.

516
00:40:16,960 --> 00:40:19,079
You have to treat him
with respect from now on.

517
00:40:19,080 --> 00:40:20,559
Understand?

518
00:40:20,560 --> 00:40:22,712
Father, I’ll remember that.

519
00:40:23,560 --> 00:40:26,679
Both of you are 20 years old now.

520
00:40:26,680 --> 00:40:30,326
According to Shaoyang’s rules, you have to
train for a year in the real world

521
00:40:30,327 --> 00:40:32,999
to gain experience and
build your personality.

522
00:40:33,000 --> 00:40:36,416
You’ll train together with Min Yan
in the real world after a few days.

523
00:40:37,016 --> 00:40:39,679
- Great! We can go down to play now!
- Great!

524
00:40:39,680 --> 00:40:42,919
I didn’t ask you to go there to play.

525
00:40:42,920 --> 00:40:46,959
If you see any demons attacking
people or criminals causing troubles,

526
00:40:46,960 --> 00:40:49,774
you have to fulfil your duty
as a cultivator.

527
00:40:49,775 --> 00:40:54,040
Don’t do anything that will humiliate
our Shaoyang Sect. Understand?

528
00:40:54,577 --> 00:40:57,217
- Yes, father.
- Yes, father.

529
00:41:03,520 --> 00:41:04,739
Junior.

530
00:41:05,280 --> 00:41:06,511
Fifth Senior.

531
00:41:06,512 --> 00:41:09,911
All of your things in Xuyang Peak
have been sent back here.

532
00:41:09,912 --> 00:41:11,433
Thank you, Fifth Senior.

533
00:41:24,120 --> 00:41:25,493
Si Feng.

534
00:41:27,320 --> 00:41:29,112
Si Feng, are you there?

535
00:41:56,905 --> 00:41:58,318
Si Feng.

536
00:41:59,840 --> 00:42:01,200
Si Feng.

537
00:42:02,240 --> 00:42:03,890
Si Feng, are you there?

538
00:42:18,248 --> 00:42:23,359
Little Phoenix. Looks like you’ve
improved a lot when I was away.

539
00:42:23,360 --> 00:42:24,800
Brother Liu?

540
00:42:25,440 --> 00:42:28,364
Why are you here?
What if others found out?

541
00:42:29,480 --> 00:42:32,639
I have the celestial eye now.

542
00:42:32,640 --> 00:42:34,919
What can Lize Palace do to me?

543
00:42:34,920 --> 00:42:36,599
You’ve succeeded?

544
00:42:36,600 --> 00:42:39,239
This celestial eye is useless
in the heavenly realm.

545
00:42:39,240 --> 00:42:40,600
They don’t need it.

546
00:42:40,601 --> 00:42:43,711
Even since it’s made,
it has been discarded to the side.

547
00:42:43,712 --> 00:42:46,559
So, I just found it purely by accident.

548
00:42:46,560 --> 00:42:48,119
So, I borrowed it from them.

549
00:42:48,120 --> 00:42:51,050
After I find Yu’Er,
I’ll just return it to them.

550
00:42:51,051 --> 00:42:52,633
They won’t know.

551
00:42:53,305 --> 00:42:55,474
Have you found Yu’Er then?

552
00:43:02,120 --> 00:43:05,680
Yu’Er must be still trapped by
her kidnapper. They blocked her aura.

553
00:43:06,864 --> 00:43:11,199
But the real reason is, I just got this
celestial eye and I can’t use it well yet.

554
00:43:11,200 --> 00:43:13,176
I can only feel a faint trace of her.

555
00:43:13,177 --> 00:43:16,791
And it takes a lot of energy to open it.
I can’t open it the second time at once.

556
00:43:16,792 --> 00:43:19,670
So, I can only look around with
the faint trace that I felt.

557
00:43:21,120 --> 00:43:25,812
In the past, I didn’t
do my duty as a father.

558
00:43:26,663 --> 00:43:30,575
So this time, I have to find her
no matter what.

559
00:43:30,576 --> 00:43:32,119
Be patient, Brother Liu.

560
00:43:32,120 --> 00:43:35,920
Since you already got the Celestial Eye,
you’ll find Yu’Er eventually.

561
00:43:50,856 --> 00:43:53,799
You are wearing this mask because of me.

562
00:43:53,800 --> 00:43:56,064
But don’t worry. I’ll definitely

563
00:43:56,065 --> 00:43:59,120
help you to find a way to
remove this Loveless Mask.
